vote.title: An ordinance abandoning a walkway to Bhakta Family Trust, the abutting owner, containing approximately 650 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Davis Street and Van Buren Avenue; and authorizing the quitclaim - Revenue: General Capital Reserve Fund ($18,025.00) and General Fund ($20,000.00), plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
